window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>How do you defeat a vicious Dungeon Master with power over all the dungeons in the world?</p> <p>This is the question that confronts me and my team after our journey to Cozocomo. The Vann family has struck so hard that it throws the fate of the entire world into question. With dungeons overflowing everywhere, it’s up to us to stop them for good.</p> <p>I’m going to need the help of all my allies if we’re going to make our last stand. I didn’t come this far just to lose now, and no matter what happens, I will stop the Vanns from achieving total domination.</p> <p>Even if that means I have to pay the ultimate price.</p> <p>Join me now for the final conclusion to the Dungeon Heroes saga!</p>"; 
